text: Hans Neuerburg (2 November 1932 – 2004) was a German footballer who played for Sportfreunde 05 Saarbrücken and the Saarland national team as a goalkeeper. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:2004 deaths Category:German footballers Category:Saar footballers Category:Saarland international footballers Category:Sportfreunde 05 Saarbrücken players Category:Association football goalkeepers
